  "subject": "Bump jasmine-core from 4.0.1 to 4.6.1",
  "commit_message": "Bump jasmine-core from 4.0.1 to 4.6.1\n\n## Release notes\n\nSourced from jasmine-core's releases.\n\n4.6.1\nPlease see the release notes.\n4.6.0\nPlease see the release notes.\n4.5.0\nPlease see the release notes.\n4.4.0\nPlease see the release notes.\n4.3.0\nPlease see the release notes.\n4.2.0\nPlease see the release notes.\n4.1.1\nPlease see the release notes.\n4.1.0\nPlease see the release notes.\n\n## Commits\n\ne4f8669 Bump version to 4.6.1\n26be252 Removed unnecessary throw when building stack trace\n2a1b7a0 Fix Chrome on CI\n4c8a4f2 Built distribution\n8bc95ae Skip parsing cause if it is not an Error object\n80b9d6c CI: Use a globally-unique Sauce tunnel ID\n66ffb5f Accessibility: Always provide a non-color indication that a spec is pending\n225194c Accessibility: Improved contrast of version number and inactive tab links\n7a75cc7 Updated copyright date\nec7a9e2 Fixed formatting of copyright notice in README\nAdditional commits viewable in compare view\n\n![Dependabot compatibility score](https://docs.github.com/en/github/managing-security-vulnerabilities/about-dependabot-security-updates#about-compatibility-scores)\n\nIssue-ID: CIMAN-33\nSigned-off-by: dependabot[bot] <support@github.com>\nSigned-off-by: onap.gh2gerrit <releng+onap-gh2gerrit@linuxfoundation.org>\nChange-Id: I013aa8fe8b5f692bb0a040ccb821d20fdf505567\nGitHub-PR: https://github.com/onap/portal-ng-ui/pull/135\nGitHub-Hash: 08d050546fa65e18\n",
